oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry star Lester Flatt at the Liberty Elementary School (17033)

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Lester Flatt and the Osborne Brothers at the Liberty Elementary School No. 1 on November 5. Poster features metal photoplates of Lester Flatts and the Osborne Brothers. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/28019.
